      "description": "Cancellation Rule: Flexible\nThis perfectly amazing bedroom overlooks the weekly Sunday Montreal Parc Jeanne Mance fields and the Tam Tam's. Enjoy the beauty and nature of Mount Royal park. Panoramic views from the top after a brisk walk or run through this dense inner city forest.\r\n\r\nA great way to start or end your day with an invigorating yet peaceful walk. Also a popular picnic spot, you could walk to Beaver lake located about 15 minutes past the beautiful Chateau and panoramic view point. This park was originally designed by Frederick Law Olmsted, the same architect who designed Central Park, (also in Boston) and has seen grown to include more statues, pavillions, and wonderful hiking paths. This 101 hectare park boosts Montreals highest peak and is right at your front door with the crucifix on the top !\r\n\r\nWe have availability at our bedroom if you are visiting for any of the major Montreal festivals, conferences and events.\r\n\r\nDrink wine purchased from the SAQ around the corner on the front yards picnic table while the sun shines on your breakfast.\r\n\r\nIn February, celebrate the Rendez-vous du cinma qubcois, Festival Nouvelles Musiques, Festival Montral en Lumire aka High Lights Festival  ends with the Nuit Blanche.\r\n\r\nThe International Children's Film Festival also coincides with students' spring break, so book early.\r\n\r\nLest we never forget the 188th annual Saint Patricks Day parade that impresses the masses of blended green adornments along Sherbrooke Street a few minutes walk away.\r\n\r\nOptional pick up from airport or train station after 5:30pm or anytime on the weekend. Just ask. We look forward to hosting your stay with us. Please feel free to ask me any kind of question you have in mind.\r\n\r\nPROPERTY INFORMATION:\r\n* Shared apartment with 3 other people maximum with your own defined bedroom area\r\n* Sofa can be used as an extra double bed\r\n* 1 bathroom\r\n* Full kitchen\r\n\r\nFEATURES:\r\n- Hardwood floors\r\n- Fully furnished\r\n- Insuite laundry\r\n- Fan in the summer and heat in the winter included.\r\n- Coffee machine, toaster, microwave, oven\r\n- TV and DVD player\r\n- Watch thousands of movies and shows on Netflix\r\n- Iron, Scale to weigh you luggage, hairdryer are available.\r\n- 220V to 110V adapters available upon request\r\n- Beautiful environment\r\n- All linens and kitchen needs included\r\n- Fully furnished with style\r\n- Free laundry\r\n\r\nPROPERTY OUTDOORS\r\n- Outdoor common BBQ area with picnic table\r\n",
