      "description": "Cancellation Rule: Strict\nVery comfortable apartment in the heart of the Plateau, located 2 minutes from Mont-Royal avenue and subway. You can hardly find a better spot in town !!! Nice living & dining room (LCD, satellite,Internet), bedroom, kitchen, bathroom with tub and shower, right in front of a little park with a very nice view. Sunny apartement with air conditionning, washer & dryer; ideal for anyone wanting to experience Montreal's unique culture. Can comfortably accommodate 3-4 people. All shops and services (coffees, bakeries, supermarket, pharmacy, fashion stores, bars, restaurants) are located just few steps away. Easy public transportation : Mont-Royal metro (100m) and BIXI (bicycle rental from Montreal) to provide access to nearby major cultural sites in minutes. You'll mostly love living in the Plateau for its variety of hip restaurants, night clubs and bars. You are also 15 min walk from the beautiful Parc Lafontaine. The apartment is fully equipped and includes a satellite flat screen TV with channels in French and English. Wi-fi Internet included. \r\nWeekly rental available at: 875 $/ week \r\n(minimum of 3 nights & possibility of longer rent, price to be discussed )",
